This paper focuses on large-scale document retrieval with high recall, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). The paper presents a visual analytics system for interactive search space reduction using targeted topic modeling based on nonnegative matrix factorization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.DL (Machine Learning).
